<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="301" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="301">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="301">
Mexico (Chiapas, new state record; Oaxaca), Guatemala, El Salvador (
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.32870/dugesiana.v6i2.3914" author="Arce-Perez, A" journalOrPublisher="Dugesiana" pageId="0" pageNumber="301" pagination="69 - 104" refId="B6" refString="Arce-Perez, A, Roughley, RE, 1999. Lista anotada y claves para los Hydradephaga (Coleoptera: Adephaga: Dytiscidae, Noteridae, Haliplidae, Gyrinidae) de Mexico. Dugesiana 6 (2): 69 - 104, DOI: https://doi.org/10.32870/dugesiana.v6i2.3914" title="Lista anotada y claves para los Hydradephaga (Coleoptera: Adephaga: Dytiscidae, Noteridae, Haliplidae, Gyrinidae) de Mexico." url="https://doi.org/10.32870/dugesiana.v6i2.3914" volume="6" year="1999">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Arce-Pérez">Arce-Perez</normalizedToken>
and Roughley 1999
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.1603/0013-8746(2001)094[0769:PDBCDO]2.0.CO;2" author="Larson, DJ" journalOrPublisher="NRC Research Press, Ottawa" pageId="0" pageNumber="301" refId="B51" refString="Larson, DJ, Alarie, Y, Roughley, RE, 2000. Predaceous diving beetles (Coleoptera: Dytiscidae) of the Nearctic Region, with emphasis on the fauna of Canada and Alaska. NRC Research Press, Ottawa, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1603/0013-8746(2001)094[0769:PDBCDO]2.0.CO;2" title="Predaceous diving beetles (Coleoptera: Dytiscidae) of the Nearctic Region, with emphasis on the fauna of Canada and Alaska." url="https://doi.org/10.1603/0013-8746(2001)094[0769:PDBCDO]2.0.CO;2" year="2000">Larson et al. 2000</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Hendrich, L" journalOrPublisher="Mitteilungen der Muenchner Entomologischen Gesellschaft" pageId="0" pageNumber="301" pagination="5 - 8" refId="B39" refString="Hendrich, L, Megna, YS, Balke, M., 2018. First record of Platambus Thomson, 1860 from Salvador (Coleoptera: Dytiscidae: Agabini). Mitteilungen der Muenchner Entomologischen Gesellschaft 108: 5 - 8" title="First record of Platambus Thomson, 1860 from Salvador (Coleoptera: Dytiscidae: Agabini)." volume="108" year="2018">Hendrich et al. 2018</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Nilsson, AN" journalOrPublisher="Dugesiana" pageId="0" pageNumber="301" publicationUrl="http://www.waterbeetles.eu" refId="B75" refString="Nilsson, AN, Hajek, J, 2020. A World Catalogue of the Family Dytiscidae, or the Diving Beetles (Coleoptera, Adephaga). Version 1.I.2020. National Museum, Prague. http://www.waterbeetles.eu" title="A World Catalogue of the Family Dytiscidae, or the Diving Beetles (Coleoptera, Adephaga). Version 1. I. 2020. National Museum, Prague." url="http://www.waterbeetles.eu" year="2020">
Nilsson and 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Hájek">Hajek</normalizedToken>
2020
</bibRefCitation>
). Previous altitudinal records are between 1,950 and 2,743 m (
<bibRefCitation author="Hendrich, L" journalOrPublisher="Mitteilungen der Muenchner Entomologischen Gesellschaft" pageId="0" pageNumber="301" pagination="5 - 8" refId="B39" refString="Hendrich, L, Megna, YS, Balke, M., 2018. First record of Platambus Thomson, 1860 from Salvador (Coleoptera: Dytiscidae: Agabini). Mitteilungen der Muenchner Entomologischen Gesellschaft 108: 5 - 8" title="First record of Platambus Thomson, 1860 from Salvador (Coleoptera: Dytiscidae: Agabini)." volume="108" year="2018">Hendrich et al. 2018</bibRefCitation>
), while in the present study the species ranged from levels 4 (river 2, 1,619m) to 4 (river 2, 1,776 m).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="301" type="comments">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="301">Comments.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="301">Collected on macrophytes and leaf packs, throughout the sampling period (February 2018 through February 2019, dry and rainy season); also collected with a bucket light trap.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
